&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;For example, &quot;last_completed_time: 151378044&quot;, it is not convenient to convert the time &quot;151378044&quot; to some human readable time, but you can calculate it via &quot;time_since_last_completed: 22 seconds&quot;, means the &quot;last_completed_time&quot; is equal to &quot;current time - 22 seconds&quot;.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
